OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779397867
OL,3,CMy brother was 'crushed by lack of
OL,4,Cpolice work' over killer Creswell
OL,6,FThe brother of a man who took his own
OL,7,Flife after raising concerns about
OL,8,Fkiller Jonathan Creswell has said that
OL,9,Fthe system has let his brother down,
OL,10,Fand he wants a public inquiry.
OL,12,FKatie Simpson, 21, from Tynan, Co
OL,13,FArmagh, died in Altnagelvin Area
OL,14,FHospital almost a week after an
OL,15,Fincident in Gortnessy Meadows,
OL,16,FLettershandoney. Police originally
OL,17,Fthought she had taken her own life.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
