PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779397867
OL,3,CMy brother was 'crushed by lack of
OL,4,Cpolice work' over killer Creswell
OL,6,FIt was not until the following year
OL,7,Fthat Jonathan Creswell, the partner of
OL,8,FMs Simpson's sister, was arrested on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,11,FA review found that "institutional
OL,12,Fmisogyny" contributed to "clear
OL,13,Fwarning signs" being missed in the
OL,14,Finitial PSNI investigation.
OL,16,FPaul Lusby knew Creswell and raised
OL,17,Fthe alarm with police after Katie was
OL,18,Fadmitted to hospital. The same review
OL,19,Ffound that Paul's interview was not
OL,20,Fproperly recorded.
OL,26,@sD@UOUtD@IO]tD@ZOUuD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
