CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779397867
OL,3,CMy brother was 'crushed by lack of
OL,4,Cpolice work' over killer Creswell
OL,6,FThe father-of-four took his own life
OL,7,Fin July 2022.
OL,9,FHis brother David Lusby described him
OL,10,Fas a "great guy, a gentleman, he was
OL,11,Fvery charismatic, very hardworking".
OL,13,F"He was a family man and he was a very
OL,14,Fproud father."
OL,16,FPaul claimed that David was "slowly
OL,17,Fbut surely crushed by the PSNI, by the
OL,18,Flack of police work."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779397867
OL,3,CMy brother was 'crushed by lack of
OL,4,Cpolice work' over killer Creswell
OL,6,F"I know from speaking to people who he
OL,7,Fwas close to that it did affect him a
OL,8,Flot.
OL,10,F"I would say in the back of his mind,
OL,11,Fhe would have been worried that it
OL,12,Fwould happen again," he added.
OL,14,F"He tried to make as much noise as
OL,15,Fpossible. He hounded quite a few
OL,16,Fpeople, not just the police, he
OL,17,Fhounded councillors and journalists,
OL,18,Fand no one was listening to him.
OL,20,F"That must have been very
OL,21,Foverwhelming, to say the least."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779397867
OL,3,CMy brother was 'crushed by lack of
OL,4,Cpolice work' over killer Creswell
OL,6,FPaul has called for a full independent
OL,7,Fpublic inquiry as he wants to know why
OL,8,Fhis brother was ignored.
OL,10,F"I want to know why a three-hour
OL,11,Fstatement was shredded. Who did that?
OL,12,FI want to know the police officer that
OL,13,Fdid that, and I guarantee he's happily
OL,14,Fretired now.
OL,16,F"I think his story needs to be told,
OL,17,Fwhich is what I'm doing now. I think
OL,18,Fthe more attention this gets, the
OL,19,Fbetter. I think that's what he
OL,20,Fdeserves. I know he would do it for
OL,21,Fme."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779397867
OL,3,CMy brother was 'crushed by lack of
OL,4,Cpolice work' over killer Creswell
OL,6,FThe PSNI said they "acknowledge the
OL,7,Fsuffering and pain of the Lusby
OL,8,Ffamily."
OL,10,FThey added: "In recent weeks both
OL,11,FAssistant Chief Constable Davy Beck
OL,12,Fand the Chief Constable Jon Boutcher
OL,13,Fhave apologised for the failings of
OL,14,Fthe PSNI into the initial
OL,15,Finvestigation into the death of Katie
OL,16,FSimpson.
OL,18,F"Earlier this month Dr Jan Melia
OL,19,Fpublished her independent review into
OL,20,Fthe case of Jonathan Creswell and the
OL,21,Fdeath of Katie Simpson."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779397867
OL,3,CMy brother was 'crushed by lack of
OL,4,Cpolice work' over killer Creswell
OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable Davy Beck
OL,7,Fsaid: "The PSNI missed opportunities.
OL,8,FWarning signs were not fully
OL,9,Frecognised early enough.
OL,11,F"We did not listen to some of those
OL,12,Fwho raised early concerns, they got it
OL,13,Fright and we were too slow to respond
OL,14,Fto their concerns that was wrong," he
OL,15,Fadded.
OL,26,@oD@GOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779397867
OL,3,CMy brother was 'crushed by lack of
OL,4,Cpolice work' over killer Creswell
OL,6,F"Patterns of coercive control were not
OL,7,Fsufficiently understood or challenged.
OL,8,FInvestigative decisions did not always
OL,9,Freflect the level of professional
OL,10,Fcuriosity and rigor that should have
OL,11,Fbeen applied.
OL,13,F"The failings are clear. We fell
OL,14,Fshort. For that, I am truly sorry.
OL,16,F"The Police Service of Northern
OL,17,FIreland as an organisation will take
OL,18,Flearnings from our failures into our
OL,19,Finitial investigation into Katie's
OL,20,Fdeath."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779397867
OL,3,CMy brother was 'crushed by lack of
OL,4,Cpolice work' over killer Creswell
OL,6,FChief Executive of the Police
OL,7,FOmbudsman's Office, Hugh Hume said:
OL,8,F"We recognise the grief and heartbreak
OL,9,Fexperienced by the Lusby family, and
OL,10,Fby Katie Simpson's family.
OL,12,F"When Paul first contacted us, we
OL,13,Fassessed whether his complaint was one
OL,14,Fthat was within our remit to
OL,15,Finvestigate. Among the criteria which
OL,16,Fhad to be considered was whether he
OL,17,Fwas personally involved in the
OL,18,Fincident, or was acting on behalf of
OL,19,Fsomeone who was.
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779397867
OL,3,CMy brother was 'crushed by lack of
OL,4,Cpolice work' over killer Creswell
OL,6,F"While our initial assessment was that
OL,7,Fthe complaint was not within our remit
OL,8,Fto investigate, we offered advice on
OL,9,Fhow the matter might be progressed.
OL,10,FPaul subsequently provided additional
OL,11,Finformation, which allowed us to
OL,12,Finvestigate a new complaint," he added.
OL,14,F"We are grateful that he brought these
OL,15,Fissues to our attention, and his
OL,16,Fcomplaint was one of a number which
OL,17,Fprompted a detailed investigation of
OL,18,Fthe police handling of Katie's death.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779397867
OL,3,CMy brother was 'crushed by lack of
OL,4,Cpolice work' over killer Creswell
OL,6,F"A response to a media query issued by
OL,7,Fthe Office in 2021 did not fully
OL,8,Freflect all of these circumstances,
OL,9,Fand was subsequently clarified.
OL,11,F"Although the review report correctly
OL,12,Fstated that complainants do not have
OL,13,Fto be family members to make a
OL,14,Fcomplaint, we did not have an
OL,15,Fopportunity to provide context prior
OL,16,Fto its publication.
OL,18,F"I will be contacting the Lusby family
OL,19,Fto offer a meeting to discuss the
OL,20,Fmatters raised, and I hope this will
OL,21,Fallow me to address their concerns."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUzD@AOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/12
